{"tid":1641691,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如何拆穿有非警察混入警隊","createTime":"2019-10-09T12:09:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T12:33:59.000Z","uid":270798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cf69cb059ed13597cc13234d57da53dab34abb0d","tid":1641691,"uid":270798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T12:09:01.000Z","msg":"可唔可以實行網上自稱懲教職員所教的方案<br />\n<br />\n有無辦法集中火力捉幾個防暴，除低佢面具，影低相，要佢講出自己姓名/編號/所屬警署/分組/小隊。講唔出就證明有非香港警察混入警隊。"},{"pid":"67ffc76860917b734edb135d501c1616811a43c8","tid":1641691,"uid":284463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T12:33:59.000Z","msg":"另類連儂牆 家家戶戶都知道<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1641528\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1641528</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}